WEBVTT

00:00:29.586 --> 00:00:31.586
like the British Virgin Islands,

00:00:31.610 --> 00:00:35.282
for rich and powerful people
who like to keep secrets.

00:00:36.195 --> 00:00:39.733
John Doe had managed to copy
every spreadsheet from this firm,

00:00:39.757 --> 00:00:41.351
every client file,

00:00:41.375 --> 00:00:43.074
every email,

00:00:43.098 --> 00:00:45.877
from 1977 to the present day.

00:00:46.912 --> 00:00:49.227
It represented the biggest cache

00:00:49.251 --> 00:00:52.037
of inside information
into the tax haven system

00:00:52.061 --> 00:00:53.589
that anyone had ever seen.

00:00:54.092 --> 00:00:58.940
But it also presented a gigantic challenge
to investigative journalism.

00:00:59.870 --> 00:01:03.802
Think about it:
11.5 million documents,